OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1780341072
OL,3,CCasualty winched to safety after
OL,4,Cgetting trapped on cliff retrieving bag
OL,6,FA casualty who ended up trapped on a
OL,7,Fnarrow cliff ledge when trying to
OL,8,Fretrieve a lost bag has been winched
OL,9,Fto safety by the Coastguard.
OL,11,FThe rescue took place at Pigeon Hole
OL,12,Fin Flamborough on Friday 29 May when
OL,13,Fthe person climbed down the cliff face
OL,14,Fto recover the bag which had fallen
OL,15,Fand realised they couldn't get back
OL,16,Fup, leaving them on a precarious ledge
OL,17,Fabove the sea.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
