FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1780341072
OL,3,CCasualty winched to safety after
OL,4,Cgetting trapped on cliff retrieving bag
OL,6,FWhen Coastguard teams from Bridlington
OL,7,Fand Filey arrived at the scene they
OL,8,Fjudged the location too dangerous for
OL,9,Fa normal cliff rescue and instead
OL,10,Frequested a helicopter to attend.
OL,12,FA spokesperson said: "As the casualty
OL,13,Fwaited anxiously on the cliff edge,
OL,14,FCoastguard teams remained in constant
OL,15,Fcontact, offering reassurance until
OL,16,Fthe helicopter appeared into view
OL,17,Foverhead."
OL,19,FThe aircraft safely winched the
OL,20,Fcasualty from the cliff before landing
OL,21,Fnearby. The person was uninjured.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
