FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1780341072
OL,3,CCasualty winched to safety after
OL,4,Cgetting trapped on cliff retrieving bag
OL,6,FBridlington Coastguard said the
OL,7,Fincident served as a "stark reminder"
OL,8,Fabout the dangers of cliffs.
OL,10,FIt said: "No matter how familiar you
OL,11,Fthink you are with the cliffs,
OL,12,Fattempting to climb down is incredibly
OL,13,Fdangerous and can put not only your
OL,14,Fown life at risk, but also the lives
OL,15,Fof Coastguard teams and helicopter
OL,16,Fcrews who may have to rescue you."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
